{"id": "1427438061041487913", "channel_id": "1400749543288475770", "type": 0, "author_id": "495650534905085962", "author_name": "niamaru.", "author_bot": false, "content": "i believe her ult multi hit triggers red stance tents on each hit meaning its alot of dmg", "timestamp": "2025-10-13T23:29:14.269000+00:00", "edited_timestamp": null, "pinned": false, "mentions": [], "reactions": [{"emoji": "👍", "emoji_id": null, "count": 1}], "attachments": [], "embeds": [], "reply_to": null, "has_thread": false, "thread_id": null, "flags": 0}
{"id": "1427439945974284298", "channel_id": "1400749543288475770", "type": 19, "author_id": "693983290423509042", "author_name": "climbkaly", "author_bot": false, "content": "With Sorel, before you exalt her:\n\n1. You want some Embryos in your hand (babies). \n2. You want to switch into Red Stance (tentacles).\n\nSorel + Blue do a lot more damage. You don't really play the blue unit cards. They are on your team to give you the blue realm mechanic of tentacles.", "timestamp": "2025-10-13T23:36:43.672000+00:00", "edited_timestamp": null, "pinned": false, "mentions": ["457756449884340225"], "reactions": [], "attachments": [{"id": "1427439944850214942", "filename": "Sorel_Blue.mp4", "content_type": "video/mp4", "size": 22008111, "url": "https://cdn.discordapp.com/attachments/1400749543288475770/1427439944850214942/Sorel_Blue.mp4?ex=6a35d28b&is=6a34810b&hm=105e20ccbbc158137252b3c33463fd8da4db29284c88e856ee2def4706fcbf93&"}], "embeds": [], "reply_to": "1427437154757247046", "has_thread": false, "thread_id": null, "flags": 0}
{"id": "1427440215936598026", "channel_id": "1400749543288475770", "type": 0, "author_id": "693983290423509042", "author_name": "climbkaly", "author_bot": false, "content": "To use Aigis properly, you have 1 baby in your hand before you exalt her.", "timestamp": "2025-10-13T23:37:48.036000+00:00", "edited_timestamp": null, "pinned": false, "mentions": [], "reactions": [], "attachments": [], "embeds": [], "reply_to": null, "has_thread": false, "thread_id": null, "flags": 0}
{"id": "1427440423357386973", "channel_id": "1400749543288475770", "type": 0, "author_id": "495650534905085962", "author_name": "niamaru.", "author_bot": false, "content": "kaly uh at some point in act 1 they sadly do need a aoe multi hit unit to break the barrier? the negate x hits thingy without that sorel struggles alooot there<:dead:1356082627509092372>", "timestamp": "2025-10-13T23:38:37.489000+00:00", "edited_timestamp": null, "pinned": false, "mentions": [], "reactions": [], "attachments": [], "embeds": [], "reply_to": null, "has_thread": false, "thread_id": null, "flags": 0}
{"id": "1427440918092447806", "channel_id": "1400749543288475770", "type": 0, "author_id": "693983290423509042", "author_name": "climbkaly", "author_bot": false, "content": "They are so early on in the game that they can just play around and have fun.\n\nTheir teams can be Salv or Uvash or Sorel for Caro...and Sorel Blue should be the easiest starting point. \n\nEventually all teams need some subs to beat certain levels, so not really an issue. They will have to figure it out as they play.", "timestamp": "2025-10-13T23:40:35.443000+00:00", "edited_timestamp": null, "pinned": false, "mentions": [], "reactions": [], "attachments": [], "embeds": [], "reply_to": null, "has_thread": false, "thread_id": null, "flags": 0}
{"id": "1427441424441540629", "channel_id": "1400749543288475770", "type": 19, "author_id": "693983290423509042", "author_name": "climbkaly", "author_bot": false, "content": "Note you can also do a Helot team to start, but she will drop off in power in the mid game. \n\nJust play around and have fun for now. Until Chapter 5, you can almost play anything. So choose the units you like the most to play with.", "timestamp": "2025-10-13T23:42:36.166000+00:00", "edited_timestamp": null, "pinned": false, "mentions": ["457756449884340225"], "reactions": [], "attachments": [], "embeds": [], "reply_to": "1427433646524072016", "has_thread": false, "thread_id": null, "flags": 0}
